  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/67e6f0df5635303141cbd1cca0e400a8.avif?t=1769772148\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ALVO VR – Redefining VR Cross‑Platform Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A high‑octane multiplayer shooter built for players who want speed, strategy, and seamless cross‑platform action. Whether you’re on PSVR1, PSVR2, Quest, Pico, or SteamVR, ALVO brings everyone together in one shared battlefield. Your headset doesn’t limit you — it connects you. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from six distinct modes, each offering a different style of combat:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Training</strong> – Hone your skills against AI.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free‑for‑All</strong> – Every player for themselves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team Deathmatch</strong> – Classic squad‑vs‑squad firefights.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Search and Destroy</strong> – Tactical, high‑stakes objective play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hardpoint</strong> – Hold the zone, control the chaos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zombies</strong> – Survive waves of the undead with your squad.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Accessibility</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ALVO is built to adapt to <i>you</i>. Choose between manual or button reloads, customize your HUD elements, and even change the entire UI color theme. Play sitting or standing — your comfort, your style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/216bb262b7021c5f88463629e04a24f4.avif?t=1769772148\" width=1560 height=568 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Weapons & Equipment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress through the ranks to unlock new gear and expand your arsenal. Customize your loadouts with:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scopes & reticles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lasers & attachments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon skins</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trinkets & cosmetic upgrades</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/f2f96b7a16f09285d7c8aa786fa7e349.poster.avif?t=1769772148\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/f2f96b7a16f09285d7c8aa786fa7e349.webm?t=1769772148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/f2f96b7a16f09285d7c8aa786fa7e349.mp4?t=1769772148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Perks</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip up to two perks to shape your playstyle. Need more stamina? Extra ammo? A little explosive resistance? Build the advantage that fits your approach to combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/1322b019da3f3b2abb60efdbd6ef681b.webp?t=1769772148\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/1322b019da3f3b2abb60efdbd6ef681b.poster.avif?t=1769772148\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=427 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Killstreaks</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn consecutive kills to unleash powerful support options. Trigger different Killstreaks at <strong>3, 5, and 7 kills</strong> to turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/7c8d8acc2cde6836a384a795425ceb6a.avif?t=1769772148\" width=1560 height=568 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Maps</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ALVO features <strong>14 core maps</strong>, with <strong>4 day/night variants</strong> for added variety. From tight urban streets to wide‑open outdoor arenas, every map is designed for fast, tactical VR combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/7a5197a54b0ec4c3ac7af90fceccdd32.webp?t=1769772148\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/7a5197a54b0ec4c3ac7af90fceccdd32.poster.avif?t=1769772148\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=427 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To enhance the experience even further, ALVO supports <strong>community‑made maps</strong>. Expand the fight with custom maps crafted by the community through our private match feature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/40224bd0f5c4fda3e69e03e1fe3b9aed.avif?t=1769772148\" width=1560 height=568 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/67e6f0df5635303141cbd1cca0e400a8.avif?t=1769772148\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ALVO VR – Redefining VR Cross‑Platform Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A high‑octane multiplayer shooter built for players who want speed, strategy, and seamless cross‑platform action. Whether you’re on PSVR1, PSVR2, Quest, Pico, or SteamVR, ALVO brings everyone together in one shared battlefield. Your headset doesn’t limit you — it connects you. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from six distinct modes, each offering a different style of combat:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Training</strong> – Hone your skills against AI.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free‑for‑All</strong> – Every player for themselves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team Deathmatch</strong> – Classic squad‑vs‑squad firefights.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Search and Destroy</strong> – Tactical, high‑stakes objective play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hardpoint</strong> – Hold the zone, control the chaos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zombies</strong> – Survive waves of the undead with your squad.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Accessibility</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ALVO is built to adapt to <i>you</i>. Choose between manual or button reloads, customize your HUD elements, and even change the entire UI color theme. Play sitting or standing — your comfort, your style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/216bb262b7021c5f88463