ve kills to unleash powerful support options. Trigger different Killstreaks at <strong>3, 5, and 7 kills</strong> to turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/7c8d8acc2cde6836a384a795425ceb6a.avif?t=1769772148\" width=1560 height=568 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Maps</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ALVO features <strong>14 core maps</strong>, with <strong>4 day/night variants</strong> for added variety. From tight urban streets to wide‑open outdoor arenas, every map is designed for fast, tactical VR combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/7a5197a54b0ec4c3ac7af90fceccdd32.webp?t=1769772148\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/7a5197a54b0ec4c3ac7af90fceccdd32.poster.avif?t=1769772148\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=427 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To enhance the experience even further, ALVO supports <strong>community‑made maps</strong>. Expand the fight with custom maps crafted by the community through our private match feature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000590/extras/40224bd0f5c4fda3e69e03e1fe3b9aed.avif?t=1769772148\" width=1560 height=568 /></span></p>",
